        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextAlignment="Justify" Margin="101,102,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="580" Height="243" RenderTransformOrigin="0.488,0.497" Foreground="black" FontSize="16"><Run Text="Do you use search engines, such as Google, Yahoo! or Bing? Do you pay your bills online? Do you like surfing with free Wi-Fi? Do you like online shopping or reading online news?"/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="If "/><Run Language="en-in" Text="any of "/><Run Text="you"/><Run Language="en-in" Text="r answers are "/><Run Text="&quot;yes&quot; to any of these questions, there's a "/><Run Language="en-in" Text="heavy"/><Run Text=" risk that your computer, phone or tablet has been exposed to malicious software or that your online behaviour "/><Run Language="en-in" Text="is "/><Run Text="be"/><Run Language="en-in" Text="ing"/><Run Text=" "/><Run Language="en-in" Text="monitored "/><Run Text="by companies that collect and sell "/><Run Language="en-in" Text="such"/><Run Text=" information."/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="This probably sounds like bad news, but don't worry - there's still"/><Run Language="en-in" Text=" a"/><Run Text=" hope! choose one of the below icon and start surfing safely today."/></TextBlock>
